data.description:
Welcome to this stunning one-year-old resale home in the Desert Sands subdivision. Prepare to be amazed by the numerous upgrades and luxurious features that make this home truly exceptional. You will be greeted by a gourmet kitchen that will delight any culinary enthusiast. The kitchen boasts a dual-sided waterfall style quartz center island, creating a striking focal point and providing ample space for meal preparation and entertaining. The home offers multiple living spaces and a dedicated movie room awaits, offering the ultimate entertainment experience. Upstairs, you'll find all the bedroom and the spacious laundry room and loft creating a flexible space with numerous possibilities.
Centrally located, this home offers easy access to the 375, all El Paso amenities, and Fort Bliss. Potential to assume a VA loan for qualified buyers. Dont miss out on this GORGEOUS home!
